                            <comment id="14455453" author="hhuynh" created="Fri, 2 Nov 2012 10:52:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;More specifics: -Dmaven.test.failure.ignore=true isn&apos;t checked when a test fails by timing out. If a test fails normally by exception then things work correctly. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
